[[Translation:en/Manual/Server]]
This word has two offen used meanings:

[1] Server is basically a computer like one you use to browse this page, but it is running 24/7 (nonstop).

[2] Server is program running inside computer that talks (by protocol) to clients. In addition to this, it makes possible e.g. sharing data, communicating and in OpenTTD also gameplay syncing (synchronization). There are many OpenTTD servers around the globe and you can freely join unlocked ones.